ns%2Fx.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Ficons%2Fx.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ficons%2Fx.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"navbar-module__AmflrG__hoverName\">Official Twitter Channel</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"toastMesage-module__hBhiOq__main\"><div class=\"toastMesage-module__hBhiOq__toastMessages\"></div></div><main class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__main\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__backRow\"><div class=\"shared-module__omp0ma__backButton\"><a href=\"/\">← Back to Tracker</a></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__hero\"><img alt=\"Tracker Whale\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__whaleLogo\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftracker-whale.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Ftracker-whale.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftracker-whale.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/><h1 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__title\">TRACKER WHALES</h1><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__subtitle\">Private Telegram Group</p><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__requirementBadge\"><span class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__requirementText\">🐋 Requires <!-- -->10,000,000<!-- --> TRACKER</span></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__descriptionCard\"><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__descriptionText\">An exclusive community for serious TRACKER holders. Get alpha, strategy discussions, and early announcements — all token-gated via gated.fun.</p></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepsSection\"><h2 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__sectionLabel\">HOW TO JOIN</h2><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepsContainer\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepRow\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLeft\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepNumber\">01</div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLine\"></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepContent\"><h3 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepTitle\">Go to gated.fun</h3><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepDescription\">Open gated.fun — a token-gating platform built on Solana.</p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLink\" href=\"https://gated.fun\">Open gated.fun →</a></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepRow\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLeft\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepNumber\">02</div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLine\"></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepContent\"><h3 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepTitle\">Login &amp; verify your wallet</h3><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepDescription\">Connect your Solana wallet and complete identity verification on the platform.</p></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepRow\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLeft\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepNumber\">03</div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLine\"></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepContent\"><h3 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepTitle\">Hold 10,000,000 TRACKER</h3><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepDescription\">Your wallet must hold at least 10 million TRACKER tokens to qualify.</p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLink\" href=\"https://jup.ag/swap/SOL-ehipS3kn9GUSnEMgtB9RxCNBVfH5gTNRVxNtqFTBAGS?ref=yfgv2ibxy07v\">Buy TRACKER on Jupiter →</a></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepRow\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepLeft\"><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepNumber\">04</div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepContent\"><h3 class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepTitle\">Join the Telegram</h3><p class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__stepDescription\">Once verified, tap the button below to enter the private Tracker Whale group.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__ctaSection\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"page-module__jN_x4a__primaryButton\" href=\"https://gated.fun\">🔑 Verify on gated.fun</a><